<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 person">
    <p class="text-center"><%= image_tag("/images/headshot-jim-concannon.png", class: "headshot") %></p>
    <p class="text-center">James (Jim) Concannon</p>
    <p class="teal text-center">President, CEO &amp; Owner</p>
    <div class="bio">
      <p>Jim is an insurance industry executive with over 25 years of hands-on experience. He worked under both his grandfather, Emmett Concannon, and his father, Michael Concannon, where he learned the art of client management and the ins-and-outs of the insurance industry. Jim earned his BSBA in Business from the University of Tulsa, and holds a Commercial Lines Coverage Specialist designation.</p>
      <p>He lives in New York City with his husband, Jason, where he heads the east coast office for The Concannon Insurance Agency. In his spare time, Jim enjoys traveling, running half marathons and serves on the Board of Directors of the Alton, Illinois nonprofit Challenge Unlimited.</p> 
      <p><a href="mailto:jim@concannonagency.com">jim@concannonagency.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="col-md-6 person">
    <p class="text-center"><%= image_tag("/images/headshot-john-concannon.png", class: "headshot") %></p>
    <p class="text-center">John Concannon</p>
    <p class="teal text-center">Vice President &amp; Owner</p>
    <div class="bio">
      <p>With over 15 years of insurance industry experience, John oversees client relationships and new business development for The Concannon Insurance Agency.  He has earned professional certifications as a Certified Identity Theft Risk Management Specialist (CITRMS) and a Certified Insurance Service Representative (CISR).</p>
      <p>Fluent in Spanish, John has become a leading insurance specialist catering to Hispanic-owned businesses. John holds a BA from the University of Missouri-Columbia and has completed advanced studies at the Universidad Autonoma de Guadalajara in Guadalajara, Mexico. John met his wife, Adria, while living in Mexico City in 2001 and has two sons. Outside of the office, John enjoys boating at the Lake of the Ozarks, traveling to Mexico with his family, and coaching his son's baseball team.</p>
      <p><a href="mailto:john@concannonagency.com">john@concannonagency.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 person">
    <p class="text-center"><%= image_tag("/images/headshot-michael-concannon.png", class: "headshot") %></p>
    <p class="text-center">Michael Concannon</p>
    <p class="teal text-center">Consultant &amp; Owner</p>
    <div class="bio">
      <p>Michael brings over 50 years of insurance and client management experience to The Concannon Insurance Agency. In 1960, he started working as an apprentice at The Concannon Insurance Agency under his father, Emmett Concannon, and has since worked his way up to lead the organization since the 1980's.</p>
      <p>Throughout his tenure, Michael has dedicated his career to helping both established organizations and entrepreneurial individuals achieve their personal and professional dreams. Michael holds a BA from St. Louis University and lives in St. Louis, Missouri with his wife of more than 50 years, Jane. Michael is an avid boater and enjoys spending time with his nine grandchildren.</p>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class="col-md-6 person">
    <p class="text-center"><%= image_tag("/images/headshot-tammy-mayer.png", class: "headshot") %></p>
