    <p class="teal text-center">Assistant Vice President</p>
    <div class="bio">
      <p>Tammy is a veteran of the insurance business with more than 35 years of hands on industry and management expertise. She has been with The Concannon Insurance Agency since 1995 and currently serves as the Assistant Vice President where she oversees account management across enterprise and small business clients.</p>
      <p>Tammy is both a Certified Insurance Service Representative and is a Licensed Property &amp; Casualty Broker. She lives in St. Louis, Missouri with her husband, Rick, and her two children. Tammy is a passionate outdoorsman and enjoys contributing to volunteer activities throughout her community in her spare time.</p>
      <p><a href="mailto:tammy@concannonagency.com">tammy@concannonagency.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 person">
    <p class="text-center"><%= image_tag("/images/headshot-terry-leech.png", class: "headshot") %></p>
    <p class="text-center">Theresa (Terry) Leech</p>
    <p class="teal text-center">Account Manager</p>
    <div class="bio">
      <p>Terry comes to The Concannon Insurance Agency as an 18 year veteran of the insurance industry. Between 1996 to 2005, she worked as an account manager and specialist for Ohio Casualty Group. Since 2005, Terry has been working on the agency side where she has focused on business insurance as an account manager. In her spare time, Terry and her husband enjoy movies, music and traveling.</p>
      <p><a href="mailto:terry@concannonagency.com">terry@concannonagency.com</a></p>
