  <div class="col-md-6 person">
    <p class="text-center"><%= image_tag("/images/headshot-laura-brown.png", class: "headshot") %></p>
    <p class="text-center">Laura Brown</p>
    <p class="teal text-center">Account Manager</p>
    <div class="bio">
      <p>Laura is an insurance industry veteran with nearly 30 years of experience. She began her career at a boutique agency in Kirkwood, Missouri before moving onto Transamerica Insurance where she held a variety of specialist roles and built a well-rounded industry knowledge. In 1996, Laura moved back to the agency side and served as the Life, Health &amp; Securities Manager for an agency in Pacific, MO.</p>
      <p>After 10 years of managing benefits, she moved to the Commercial Lines department where she continues today with The Concannon Insurance Agency and has been a team member for over five years. Laura earned her CIC (Certified Insurance Counselor) designation in 2013. She is married with two children and enjoys camping, boating and traveling with her family.</p>
      <p><a href="mailto:laura@concannonagency.com">laura@concannonagency.com</a></p>
    </div>
