<div class="row">
  
  <div class="col-md-6 person">
    <p class="text-center"><%= image_tag("/images/headshot-michael-schrand.png", class: "headshot") %></p>
    <p class="text-center">Michael Schrand</p>
    <p class="teal text-center">Loss Control &amp; Risk Management Specialist</p>
    <div class="bio">
      <p>Michael has been working with The Concannon Insurance Agency for nearly a decade and brings with him 20+ years of professional loss control experience from numerous sectors, such as healthcare, manufacturing, construction and service industries. He is both a property assessment specialist and is an expert on reducing workers compensation costs in all industries.</p>
      <p>As a leader in the risk management field, Michael is the mastermind behind Zero Accident Culture® (ZAC®), a revolutionary program geared towards eliminating workplace injuries by systematically reducing hazards, modifying unsafe behaviors, and building an organization-wide commitment to health and safety. At The Concannon Insurance Agency, Michael provides clients with the Zero Accident Culture® program training and in-depth assistance on loss prevention and risk management. Michael holds a BS in Safety Engineering from Illinois State University and an MBA from Fontbonne University. He lives in St. Louis with his wife, Evelyn, and his three daughters.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-6 person">
