    <p class="text-center">Joe Berchelmann</p>
    <p class="teal text-center">Insurance Brokerage Specialist</p>
    <div class="bio">
      <p>Joe has forty years of experience in the insurance industry and has helped countless companies and individuals with their insurance needs. Joe has known the Concannon’s for thirty years and officially became part of their team in 2010. Highly knowledgeable and experienced, Joe has built a reputation for being an outspoken advocate for a diverse array of clients around the country. He is dedicated to helping them take advantage of the complex insurance and tax laws, while optimizing and minimizing their costs.</p> 
      <p>Joe is married with three grown children, is a graduate of St. Mary’s University, and has completed graduate work at the University of Texas. Outside of the office, Joe has enjoyed coaching collegiate baseball for sixteen years, most recently completing a twelve year tenure at Washington University in St. Louis.</p>
